      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_34419050905952990.png",
                "id": "talent59052",
                "key": "Liutian Archery",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Liutian Archery"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span><br>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ice Lotus</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Ice Lotus</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter aktifmu menerima DMG:</span> Mengurangi 1 poin DMG yang diterima.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan:</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/d3562dc7ee1b952be23d991318822774_176033540063632912.png",
                "id": "talent4705",
                "key": "Trail of the Qilin",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Trail of the Qilin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, mengakibatkan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">2 poin</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> ke seluruh Karakter standby.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/01/25750596/67d6f9d70e695a791caa42953d11e1e3_856794591262593998.png",
                "id": "talent5183",
                "key": "Frostflake Arrow",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Frostflake Arrow"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> ke seluruh Karakter standby lawan, memanggil 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sacred Cryo Pearl</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/6b78c979575a782c1625dce67992cf90_6367585924570967628.png",
                "id": "talent42212",
                "key": "Celestial Shower",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Celestial Shower"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai: </span>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> dan mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> ke seluruh Karakter standby lawan.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan:</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7116760339638898124.png",
                "id": "talent33001",
                "key": "Sacred Cryo Pearl",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/5768b83a04afeb8e581b0f7864fd39d9_5384749633762937118.png",
                "title": "Sacred Cryo Pearl"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Cryo dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_9170851306557918281.png",
                "id": "talent38222",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG tidak dapat dipengaruhi oleh Bonus DMG apa pun, namun tidak dapat dilawan oleh efek seperti Perisai dan kekebalan DMG.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7344005156370352272.png",
                "id": "talent29052",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
